{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/Lambda.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.dsimpLambda\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">DSimp</span>.<span class=\"name\">dsimpLambda</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/DSimpM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.DSimproc\">DSimproc</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Definitionally simplifies a lambda expression.\n\nUnlike `Sym.Simp.simpLambda`, it descends into the binder type as well as the\nbody.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/Lambda.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.dsimpLambda","kind":"def","line":13,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.dsimpLambda","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/DSimp/Lambda.lean#L13-L41"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym.AbstractS","Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.DSimpM","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateS"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.DSimp.Lambda"}